因為合約問題跟無綫談不攏而決意離巢。至於劉江今日亦有憑《金宵大廈》書店老闆林老師一角，獲提名角逐最佳男配角，不過劉江似乎沒有信心，只稱純粹出席撐劇集。<br />\n<br />\n劉江亦願意接受新挑戰，認為在TVB工作太久，已不熟識外面的世界，希望事業可以有更高成就，但不會做回以往做過的武師工作。<br />\n<br />\n劉江今晚憑《金宵大廈》爭奪台慶頒獎禮最佳男配角，結果他敗給24歲的周嘉洛，周嘉洛在《愛&middot;回家之開心速遞》中飾演滕麗名廢青兒子金城安，今晚他領獎時自封是廢青界巨子。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20200112/60477954\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200112%2F60477954&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXR4w7aMtX%2B%2FJ%2BUdoe8qorTI%3D&h=fc0c453a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200112%2F60477954&h=341458cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20200112/60477954</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T01:52:17.000Z","msg":"難怪走 啲獎頒咗比啲on9<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cdd3b448ba2345b14600d37d43a3e7af55578f4","tid":1821729,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e649d78d47f770f4647ccc651c4a5a3a2242cc41","tid":1821729,"uid":137999,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T01:34:04.000Z","msg":"去Viu tv拍返個節目 <br />\n<br />\nx!講呢啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T01:52:28.000Z","msg":"拍埋火火嗰啲應該幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b5622b172def34ce269d3969c760f063c776ce","tid":1821729,"uid":27882,"like":19,"dislike":34,"score":-15,"quote":{"pid":"e13448d40bf516ecdef5e0e92993090e3654c9c5","tid":1821729,"uid":49004,"like":8,"dislike":11,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"421d276616d6afcd2ea341a8e1745d508732332e","tid":1821729,"uid":130626,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T22:53:29.000Z","msg":"【男配輸畀金城安】劉江入行超過50年 台慶頒獎禮宣佈離開TVB<br />\n<br />\n今晚大台頒獎禮，賽前例牌由一班女藝人爭紅鬥艷，不過今年除了靚女，73歲的老演員劉江都是紅毯焦點，因為他行完紅毯後，向傳媒自爆後日（14日）約滿，但不會與TVB續約。<br />\n<br />\n劉江今晚與鼎爺李家鼎一齊行紅毯，氣勢