戲，拍到攰就會休息。言下之意，似另有隱情，不排除劉江因為合約問題跟無綫談不攏而決意離巢。至於劉江今日亦有憑《金宵大廈》書店老闆林老師一角，獲提名角逐最佳男配角，不過劉江似乎沒有信心，只稱純粹出席撐劇集。<br />\n<br />\n劉江亦願意接受新挑戰，認為在TVB工作太久，已不熟識外面的世界，希望事業可以有更高成就，但不會做回以往做過的武師工作。<br />\n<br />\n劉江今晚憑《金宵大廈》爭奪台慶頒獎禮最佳男配角，結果他敗給24歲的周嘉洛，周嘉洛在《愛&middot;回家之開心速遞》中飾演滕麗名廢青兒子金城安，今晚他領獎時自封是廢青界巨子。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20200112/60477954\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200112%2F60477954&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXR4w7aMtX%2B%2FJ%2BUdoe8qorTI%3D&h=fc0c453a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200112%2F60477954&h=341458cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20200112/60477954</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T01:52:17.000Z","msg":"難怪走 啲獎頒咗比啲on9<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T03:36:29.000Z","msg":"寧願佢俾terry好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb89b06b5f2df6490c89f4a04bec55fdd2c57541","tid":1821729,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94dfe1762f3472a281b9f9419fe705cb3fa72e2d","tid":1821729,"uid":334806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01d597b27dbea486e7b0198fbbbc0e21762aee41","tid":1821729,"uid":202412,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"b67a1e7cdb015dde15804f6de4fa141b763f3665","tid":1821729,"uid":33099,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T02:41:01.000Z","msg":"劉江咁既軰份叫老師都無問題啦<br />\n<br />\n戇尻係後生嗰D (40歲都未到）都叫老師啫"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T02:44:43.000Z","msg":"我唔係在地人就唔知 但好多對該行業有好高貢獻嘅人都會被叫老師"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T03:34:59.000Z","msg":"日本都係咁叫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T03:37:07.000Z","msg":"腥些<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid