接受傳媒訪問，自爆在TVB工作30幾年，但原來已經沒再簽TVB，他又說向傳媒說：「唔好問點解，我唔可以話點解。」劉江又表明自己仍然有戲癮，不會退休，亦有人建議他繼續演戲，拍到攰就會休息。言下之意，似另有隱情，不排除劉江因為合約問題跟無綫談不攏而決意離巢。至於劉江今日亦有憑《金宵大廈》書店老闆林老師一角，獲提名角逐最佳男配角，不過劉江似乎沒有信心，只稱純粹出席撐劇集。<br />\n<br />\n劉江亦願意接受新挑戰，認為在TVB工作太久，已不熟識外面的世界，希望事業可以有更高成就，但不會做回以往做過的武師工作。<br />\n<br />\n劉江今晚憑《金宵大廈》爭奪台慶頒獎禮最佳男配角，結果他敗給24歲的周嘉洛，周嘉洛在《愛&middot;回家之開心速遞》中飾演滕麗名廢青兒子金城安，今晚他領獎時自封是廢青界巨子。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20200112/60477954\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200112%2F60477954&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXR4w7aMtX%2B%2FJ%2BUdoe8qorTI%3D&h=fc0c453a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200112%2F60477954&h=341458cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20200112/60477954</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T01:52:17.000Z","msg":"難怪走 啲獎頒咗比啲on9<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T03:36:29.000Z","msg":"寧願佢俾terry好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:59:31.000Z","msg":"好似話冇配角獎"},{"pid":"dc477951ca184c0fa57015c95c2271d11ffe6ebe","tid":1821729,"uid":283006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d43cd9fce6f72169a65768fbbfd9cf634c25a61b","tid":1821729,"uid":115042,"like":164,"dislike":3,"score":161,"quote":{"pid":"35fefc224b16b7c48173b101716470714e3cded6","tid":1821729,"uid":119792,"like":65,"dislike":2,"score":63,"quote":{"pid":"d9b30240c9637a8eb77d70280a29851bca0bd4e0","tid":1821729,"uid":132587,"like":105,"dislike":4,"score":101,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T14:00:40.000Z","msg":"肯定係之前撐過黃店<br />\n有人篤灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T